snippet.title: Dogs just never fail to make us laugh - Funny dog compilation
snippet.description:
Dogs are so funny and hilarious, they just never fail to make us laugh and happy! Just look how all these dogs and puppies play, sleep, get along with cats, babies, how they fail, make funny sounds,... So funny, ridiculous and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
